               <typeofhazard class="+ topic/li hazard-d/typeofhazard ">damage to the Terminal</typeofhazard>
               <howtoavoid class="+ topic/li hazard-d/howtoavoid ">Always use screwdrivers of an appropriate size for the
push in terminal. A too large or too small screwdriver can damage
the terminal.</howtoavoid>
               <howtoavoid class="+ topic/li hazard-d/howtoavoid ">Only use flat screwdrivers and always apply pressure carefully.</howtoavoid>
            </messagepanel>
         </hazardstatement>
